"     </b>",
"     (FML Forte Ophthalmic)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     0.25% (5 mL): $38.22",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     <b>",
"      Suspension",
"     </b>",
"     (FML Liquifilm Ophthalmic)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     0.1% (5 mL): $47.09",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F172509\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Intraocular pressure in patients with glaucoma or when used for &ge;10 days; presence of secondary infections (including the development of fungal infections and exacerbation of viral infections)",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
